<br>
One thing that did surprise me, though, is the number of young callers I am getting.  I figured I wouldn't get many people under the age of 20 calling, because they probably don't remember when BBSes were popular.  But I've had quite a few callers in that age range, so I'm not sure how to explain it.<br>
<br>
Anyway, it's no big deal whether people call or not, and I'm not trying to convince anyone to visit who has no interest in it.  I just wanted to make people aware of it, so that they'd know that the good ol' door games had not completely died off. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#808080><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/udrgabe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DrGabe</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://heavyhand.org/portent-avatar.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>King of the Message Board</span><br>  Posts: 374<br> <font color=#000080>(4/1/02 4:14:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fheavyhand65062frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=141.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.heavyhand.org/HeavyHand-button03.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: BBSes</span><hr size=1> Believe me... people who were into BBS's are pure addicts to it.  Its just that not many around this board ever were and I would be surprised if any converted.  Besides, most the peeps here spend too much time downloading anime porn, *cough, Calsitra*cough. <p>Viva la Revelution!! <br>
